  "body": "English\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nThis datapack adds the crafting of an invisible block of light that is not available in survival mode\n\nTo make the datapack work, you just need to upload it to the \"datapacks\" folder of your Minecraft world\n\nGame Versions\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n- `1.21.8`\n- `1.21.7`\n- `1.21.6`\n- `1.21.5`\n- `1.21.4`\n- `1.21.3`\n- `1.21.2`\n- `1.21.1`\n\n\n- `1.20.4`\n- `1.20.3`\n- `1.20.2`\n- `1.20.1`\n\nDemonstration\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n![Crafting an invisible block of light](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/84ecec38b61ffc1acb98584d926b5f44ce4cef07.png)\n\nAuthor\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nha1reX\n\nJoin my discord server for any questions :З\n\n[Discord](https://dsc.gg/spark-mc)\n\n\n\nРусский\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nЭтот датапак добавляет крафт блока невидимого света для Minecraft Java\n\nЧтобы установить датапак, достаточно загрузить его в папку \"datapacks\" вашего мира Minecraft\n\nПоддерживаемые версии\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n- `1.21.8`\n- `1.21.7`\n- `1.21.6`\n- `1.21.5`\n- `1.21.4`\n- `1.21.3`\n- `1.21.2`\n- `1.21.1`\n\n\n- `1.20.4`\n- `1.20.3`\n- `1.20.2`\n- `1.20.1`\n\nДемонстрация\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n![Crafting an invisible block of light](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/84ecec38b61ffc1acb98584d926b5f44ce4cef07.png)\n\nАвтор\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nha1reX\n\nПрисоединяйтесь к моему Дискорд Серверу, отвечу на любые вопросы :З\n\n[Discord](https://dsc.gg/spark-mc)\n\n\n\n",
